item.title: CVE-2023-5620|2024-08-02T08:07:32.570Z -- unknown -- web%20push%20notifications
item.description: The Web Push Notifications WordPress plugin before 4.35.0 does not prevent visitors on the site from changing some of the plugin options, some of which may be used to conduct Stored XSS attacks.
